{
  "info": {
    "name": "MyPetCare Admin API",
    "description": "Collection Postman per testare gli endpoint Admin di MyPetCare (stats e refund). Richiede Environment Variables: baseUrl, adminToken, paymentId",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health Check",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["health"]
        },
        "description": "Verifica che il server backend sia attivo e funzionante"
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "GET /admin/stats",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/stats",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["admin", "stats"]
        },
        "description": "Ottiene statistiche aggregate:\n- usersTotal: Numero totale utenti\n- activePros: Numero PRO attivi\n- revenue30d: Entrate ultimi 30 giorni (€)\n- bookings30d: Prenotazioni ultimi 30 giorni\n\nRichiede: Token Firebase ID di un utente con ruolo admin"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "Success Response",
          "originalRequest": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/stats",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "stats"]
            }
          },
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"usersTotal\": 523,\n  \"activePros\": 47,\n  \"revenue30d\": 12450.00,\n  \"bookings30d\": 189\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "POST /admin/refund/:paymentId (Totale)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": ""
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/refund/{{paymentId}}",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["admin", "refund", "{{paymentId}}"]
        },
        "description": "Rimborso TOTALE di un pagamento esistente.\n\nSupporta automaticamente:\n- Stripe (charge, payment_intent, invoice)\n- PayPal (capture_id)\n\nRichiede:\n- adminToken: Token Firebase ID utente admin\n- paymentId: ID documento Firestore del pagamento\n\nNOTA: Body vuoto = rimborso totale"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "Success Response",
          "originalRequest": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": ""
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/refund/pay_abc123",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "refund", "pay_abc123"]
            }
          },
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"refund\": {\n    \"id\": \"re_1PQzEL2eZvKYlo2C0D5C9mVj\",\n    \"amount\": 2999,\n    \"status\": \"succeeded\",\n    \"created\": 1704724800\n  },\n  \"message\": \"Rimborso completato\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "POST /admin/refund/:paymentId (Parziale)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"amountCents\": 499\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/refund/{{paymentId}}",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["admin", "refund", "{{paymentId}}"]
        },
        "description": "Rimborso PARZIALE di un pagamento esistente.\n\nParametri Body:\n- amountCents (number): Importo in centesimi (es: 499 = €4.99)\n\nSupporta automaticamente:\n- Stripe (charge, payment_intent, invoice)\n- PayPal (capture_id)\n\nRichiede:\n- adminToken: Token Firebase ID utente admin\n- paymentId: ID documento Firestore del pagamento"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "Success Response",
          "originalRequest": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"amountCents\": 499\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/refund/pay_abc123",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "refund", "pay_abc123"]
            }
          },
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"refund\": {\n    \"id\": \"re_1PQzEL2eZvKYlo2C0D5C9mVj\",\n    \"amount\": 499,\n    \"status\": \"succeeded\",\n    \"created\": 1704724800\n  },\n  \"message\": \"Rimborso parziale completato (€4.99)\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "POST /admin/refund - Stripe Invoice Example",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"amountCents\": 999\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/refund/in_1PQzEL2eZvKYlo2C8KKfQjXt",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["admin", "refund", "in_1PQzEL2eZvKYlo2C8KKfQjXt"]
        },
        "description": "Esempio di rimborso su una Stripe Invoice.\n\nNOTA: Sostituisci 'in_1PQzEL2eZvKYlo2C8KKfQjXt' con un ID invoice reale dal tuo Firestore.\n\nFormato Stripe Invoice ID: in_XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX"
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "POST /admin/refund - PayPal Capture Example",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"amountCents\": 999\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/refund/8LW12345X6789012K",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["admin", "refund", "8LW12345X6789012K"]
        },
        "description": "Esempio di rimborso su un PayPal Capture.\n\nNOTA: Sostituisci '8LW12345X6789012K' con un ID capture reale dal tuo Firestore.\n\nFormato PayPal Capture ID: 17 caratteri alfanumerici"
      },
      "response": []
    }
  ],
  "event": [],
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "https://api.mypetcare.app",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "adminToken",
      "value": "YOUR_FIREBASE_ADMIN_ID_TOKEN_HERE",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "paymentId",
      "value": "PAYMENT_DOC_ID_FROM_FIRESTORE",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ]
}
